eformmail is a safe and secure CGI program that can mail the contents
of an HTML form to a user. It can do so without revealing the identify
of the recipient on the web page. For example it is not buried in a
hidden field.

The installation documentation is in (doc/)eformmail.html


Features

- Recipient email address is not specified on the web page that uses
  this program. This prevents spammers from learning that email and
  exploiting it.

- Program is written such to prevent harvesting of web pages that
  use this program in order to exploit it.

- Program does not leak any information to the outside world.

- Contents of form can be formatted with XSLT processor.

- Contains silent spam traps to weed out any spam that is being sent
  through the form.
